{"type": "article", "id": 15913, "title": "爬到高处去睡觉，你就可以给房子腾出更多地方来", "description": "床被架高了，这样就多出了一个看书和更衣的空间。", "date": "2015-10-12T10:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11871, "name": "住宅"}, {"id": 17018, "name": "小房子"}, {"id": 17019, "name": "双层"}, {"id": 5133, "name": "西班牙"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 30, "praise_count": 463, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121908QjFR0rdGwfVOm5yX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t小空间大利用的例子你可能已见过很多，<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/10/09/nookarchitects-design-the-interior-of-a-loft-apartment-in-barcelona/\" target=\"_blank\">来看看西班牙这个 <span>loft </span>的设计吧</a>：空间太小，衣柜没地方放，设计师就把床放置在了高处，床下面是一个看书和更衣的空间。不过有点奇怪的是，这个房间里的储物空间看起来很少，不知道买买买星人住进来的话，东西要往哪里放。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121859gk02CnZ95oLvjmaB.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"这个公寓名叫G-ROC，是由建筑事务所 nookarchitects 设计的\" alt=\"这个公寓名叫G-ROC，是由建筑事务所 nookarchitects 设计的\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>这个公寓名叫 G-ROC，是由建筑事务所 <a href=\"http://www.nookarchitects.com\" target=\"_blank\">nookarchitects</a> 设计的</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121859Qdqw9FElYrj5JuMD.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"它位于巴塞罗那的一个废弃的阁楼上\" alt=\"它位于巴塞罗那的一个废弃的阁楼上\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>它位于巴塞罗那的一个废弃的阁楼上</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031219007dvkanKcNL6Y3Die.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"设计师将小小的空间分隔成了“日”和“夜”\" alt=\"设计师将小小的空间分隔成了“日”和“夜”\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>设计师将小小的空间分隔成了“日”和“夜”，带床的部分是夜间使用的</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031219002E3uKQC1kmRsLoI9.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"小小的拉帘是区隔\" alt=\"小小的拉帘是区隔\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>小小的拉帘是区隔</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031219014s89Vjhwt2JnDQHF.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"从卧室空间望出去\" alt=\"从卧室空间望出去\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>从卧室空间望出去</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121901XZU7W962gbuAyoOD.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"起居室\" alt=\"起居室\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>起居室</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121902MKWBzpbuqcX2AInh.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"起居空间\" alt=\"起居空间\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>起居空间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121902zQJknblYLgNu64RS.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"屋内全景\" alt=\"屋内全景\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>屋内全景</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121903EbeDXHNw2KYG1rql.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"餐厅\" alt=\"餐厅\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>餐厅</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121904LKP4FZMv1lC9eEUf.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121904BdyqV3Wecnr527zs.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121905Eno8uUCYtT1VeZLd.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"地板的设计\" alt=\"地板的设计\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>地板的设计</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121905aiIHXVRTxwAtLE8b.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"这是该建筑工作室另一个住宅案例\" alt=\"这是该建筑工作室另一个住宅案例\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>这是该建筑工作室另一个住宅案例</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121906vAPTj7DntsMUwxr2.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"425\" title=\"也位于巴塞罗那\" alt=\"也位于巴塞罗那\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>也位于巴塞罗那</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121906hBbSTWFYJOt5GZwx.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"491\" title=\"卧室空间\" alt=\"卧室空间\" data-ratio=\"0.7671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>卧室空间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121906jncFb9UXsIu23O8w.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"244\" title=\"全景空间\" alt=\"全景空间\" data-ratio=\"0.38125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>全景空间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121907YRkMq0l2KgSCuZhi.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"巴塞罗那的另一处住宅\" alt=\"巴塞罗那的另一处住宅\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>巴塞罗那的另一处住宅</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031219077uJnUMTe3z8gptBR.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"厨房\" alt=\"厨房\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>厨房</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121907tbiHPzWfAE3m1G5x.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"起居室\" alt=\"起居室\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>起居室</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607031219086kp17aEFxOSzUqZi.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"起居空间\" alt=\"起居空间\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>起居空间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em>题图来源：</em></span><a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/10/09/nookarchitects-design-the-interior-of-a-loft-apartment-in-barcelona/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>contemporist</em></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n"}